snippet.title: Samबहादुर - Official Trailer | Vicky Kaushal | Meghna Gulzar | Ronnie S | In Cinemas 01.12.2023
snippet.description:
To the Indian army, to the nation and its people, we present to you a glimpse into the life of India's Greatest Soldier, Sam Manekshaw. 

#SamBahadur Trailer Out Now! 
#Samबहादुर in cinemas 1.12.2023

#SamIsHere 

Samबहादुर is a tribute to Field Marshal Sam HFJ Manekshaw, MC, India's first Field Marshal and a legendary Army General. His career witnessed the shaping of India's geopolitical borders, and his life was marked by significant milestones, from fighting in World War II to being the Chief of Army Staff during the 1971 Indo-Pakistan war, that led to the creation of Bangladesh.
This RSVP film explores his dynamic personality and his unparalleled military career, offering a glimpse into the life of a no-nonsense Army Commander, also known as "Sam Bahadur" by the soldiers he led.

This RSVP film explores his dynamic personality and his unparalleled military career, offering a glimpse into the life of a no-nonsense Army Commander, also known as "Sam Bahadur" by the soldiers he led.

होखे लागि भउजी हो उलटिया 
काहे फेर के सुतेलु करवटिया....

भीतरी से गच बाड़ू उपरे से गुसेलु
लड़की :- मार जनि मस्का तोहार चस्का ए पिया जान तानी
 नीलकमल एही से ना कहल तोहर मान तानी
लड़का :- मान जा ना धनी तनी बतिया
करे द रंगीन हमार रतिया
काहे फेर के सुतेलु करवटिया
                                       End.

snippet.description:
Article 51A(h) in The Constitution Of India 
It shall be the duty of every citizen of India to develop the scientific temper, humanism and the spirit of inquiry and reform.

അത്ഭുത സിദ്ധി, അമാനുഷികത എന്ന പേരിൽ സോഷ്യൽ മീഡിയ വഴി പ്രചരിക്കുന്ന  വീഡിയോകളുടെ രഹസ്യം, റീ ക്രിയേറ്റ് ചെയ്തു കാണിക്കാനോ, മറ്റേതെങ്കിലും വീഡിയോ, ഫയലുകൾ, ഉപയോഗിച്ച് അതിൻറെ രഹസ്യം തെളിയിക്കാനോ സാധിക്കുന്നത് മാത്രമേ  എപ്പിസോഡുകളിൽ ഉൾപ്പെടുത്തുകയുള്ളൂ

പുതിയ വിഡിയോ പെട്ടെന്ന് നിങ്ങളിലേക്കെത്താൻ വിഡിയോക്ക് താഴെയുള്ള SUBSCRIBE ബട്ടൻ ക്ലിക്ക് ചെയ്ത ശേഷം ബെൽ ബട്ടൺ 🔔  ക്ലിക്ക് ചെയ്യുക

snippet.title: IND Beat SA: Kohli's Triple Blast, Shoaib Akhtar Shocked! | Aakash Chopra Reaction | World Cup 2023
snippet.description:
India Beats South Africa World Cup 2023 Live Updates: In the match played between India and South Africa in the World Cup 2023, India has defeated South Africa. Batting first, Team India had given a target of 327 runs to South Africa to win. In response to which South African team was out within 100 runs. Kohli played a century for India. Shreyas Iyer played an inning of 77 runs. On the bowling front, Ravindra Jadeja took 5 wickets and Kuldeep took 2 wickets. The entire South African team could score only 83 runs. The 243-run victory, which came on the occasion of Virat Kohli's birthday, was spectacular.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3923 | 8 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3923: Babita Ke Liye Best Gift
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha ultimately tells the inhabitants of Gokuldham about his surprise present for Babita. Jetha dims the lights and produces a lunar-like atmosphere, which surprises everyone. Babita is ecstatic after learning that Jetha has some exciting plans for the actual Moon. Jetha informs Babita that he has purchased a lunar plot for her. Champaklal is taken aback and queries Jetha about it. Other Gokuldham people are skeptical about Jetha's words. Later, Bagha and Nattu Kaka disclose everything to everyone in order to back up Jetha's claim.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3923, 8 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: कैसे फिर गया Jethalal की इच्छा पर पानी | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 9 Nov 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Taarak Mehta felt like eating delicious food today. Jethalal is very excited to eat Jalebi - Fafda. Taarak Mehta comes to Jethalal's house and eats Jalebi Fafda.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 0184
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

नमस्ते दोस्तों!
Mountain Dew 'Darr Ke Aage Jeet Hai' Stories On The Ranveer Show हिंदी के 212th Episode में आप सभी का स्वागत है. आज के Podcast में हमारे साथ जुड़ चुके हैं हमारे भाई Yuvraj Singh, जो Cricket Legend हैं। हर Cricket Fan इनकी Batting Style का दीवाना रहा है। Life में कई Challenges का सामना करने के बाद भी उन्होंने अपने Darr Par Jeet Haasil की, उनकी इसी Warrior Mentality के सभी Fan हैं।

इस Podcast में हम बात करेंगे ढ़ेर सारी बातें Yuvraj Singh की Early Life, Cricket Career, Love For Golf, Family, MS Dhoni के साथ Friendship, Sachin Tendulkar और Zaheer Khan के बारे में। 

साथ ही साथ हम बात करेंगे Life After & Before Cancer, 2011 World Cup, Australia Cricket Team, Men's Mental Health और Virat Kohli की Captaincy के बारे में और भी ढ़ेर सारी बातें।

मैं आशा करता हूँ कि ये Video आप सभी Viewers को पसंद आएगा। खास तौर पर उन सभी को जिन्हें Indian Cricket Team और Cricketers के बारे में जानने में Interest है। 

Sports Culture In India, Indian Cricket Dressing Room Secrets और Young Cricket Players जैसी चीज़ों के बारे में हम Discuss करेंगे इस Hindi Podcast में सिर्फ और सिर्फ आपके Favourite BeerBiceps Hindi Channel Ranveer Allahbadia पर।

snippet.description:

snippet.description:

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal:

Jethalal is giving sweets to everyone in Gokuldham after this 1000 phone incident. Now Jethalal is going to Babita ji. Stay tuned.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 2724
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 382
snippet.description:
എന്തോ കാര്യമായി അന്വേഷിക്കുകയാണ് ലെച്ചു. അന്വേഷിച്ചു ചെന്നപ്പോൾ തനിക്ക് പ്രയോജനമില്ലാത്തതൊന്നും കൈകൊണ്ട് തൊടില്ലെന്നു ബാലു. ലെച്ചുവിന് ഇത്രയും വേണ്ടപ്പെട്ട വസ്തു കൈക്കലാക്കിയതാര്? അറിയുവാൻ മറക്കാതെ കാണുക, 'ഉപ്പും മുളകും'.  

Lechu is searching for something very important. When checked with Balu, he says he wouldn't touch anything that is of no use to him. Who has hidden the thing Lechu is looking for? To find out, watch 'Uppum Mulakum'

Today’s recipe is Diwali faral shankarpali using 1 kilo maida. It turns out nice, crispy and flaky. Diwali faral is incomplete without shankarpali. We already have seen different recipes if shankarpali. This is full proof recipe the proportion used is just perfect. It is a very easy and simple recipe. You can make it within no time. Besides, I am sharing few tips to make perfect shankarpali. This is a popular Marathi recipe. Also it can be a good tea time snack. You can try this recipe at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
• 1 cup Milk
• 1 cup Sugar
• 1 cup Ghee
• 7 cups / 1 kilo Maida
• Oil for frying

Method:
• Heat up a pan on medium heat and add milk and sugar. 
• Heat it up together until sugar is dissolved. 
• When sugar is dissolved and the mixture begins to boil, turn off the gas and add ghee. 
• Melt ghee before measuring. Make sure you don’t use thick ghee. 
• Mix well and base for shankarpali is ready. 
• Transfer the base into the maida and mix in with the help of ladle. 
• Knead the mixture into dough. 
• Make small portions of the dough. Keep the leftover dough covered with a wet cloth.
• Take one portion and roll it into a thick chapati. The thickness of the chapati should be about 1 
  cm. 
• Cut off the edges and roll the chapati little more if you want. 
• Cut shankarpali into size and shape you want and take them out into a dish. 
• Rolled out shankarpali should not dry out. 
• Heat up oil on high heat for about 5 minutes and reduce the heat to low. 
• Drop shankarpali into hot oil and fry it well for at least 3-4 minutes. 
• If oil is hot enough and still shankarpali dissolves in oil, then add a little more maida into the 
  dough. Add a little milk and knead the dough again. Roll out shankarpali and fry. It won’t dissolve. 
• When shankarpali gets nice golden color from all sides, take it out, drain excess oil and transfer it 
  into a dish. Shankarpali is ready.
• You can store them in an air tight container when they cool down completely. They have shelf life 
  of about 1 month.

Today’s recipe is Diwali faral shankarpali using 1 kilo maida. It turns out nice, crispy and flaky. Diwali faral is incomplete without shankarpali. We already have seen different recipes if shankarpali. This is full proof recipe the proportion used is just perfect. It is a very easy and simple recipe. You can make it within no time. Besides, I am sharing few tips to make perfect shankarpali. This is a popular Marathi recipe. Also it can be a good tea time snack. You can try this recipe at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
• 1 cup Milk
• 1 cup Sugar
• 1 cup Ghee
• 7 cups / 1 kilo Maida
• Oil for frying

Method:
• Heat up a pan on medium heat and add milk and sugar. 
• Heat it up together until sugar is dissolved. 
• When sugar is dissolved and the mixture begins to boil, turn off the gas and add ghee. 
• Melt ghee before measuring. Make sure you don’t use thick ghee. 
• Mix well and base for shankarpali is ready. 
• Transfer the base into the maida and mix in with the help of ladle. 
• Knead the mixture into dough. 
• Make small portions of the dough. Keep the leftover dough covered with a wet cloth.
• Take one portion and roll it into a thick chapati. The thickness of the chapati should be about 1 
  cm. 
• Cut off the edges and roll the chapati little more if you want. 
• Cut shankarpali into size and shape you want and take them out into a dish. 
• Rolled out shankarpali should not dry out. 
• Heat up oil on high heat for about 5 minutes and reduce the heat to low. 
• Drop shankarpali into hot oil and fry it well for at least 3-4 minutes. 
• If oil is hot enough and still shankarpali dissolves in oil, then add a little more maida into the 
  dough. Add a little milk and knead the dough again. Roll out shankarpali and fry. It won’t dissolve. 
• When shankarpali gets nice golden color from all sides, take it out, drain excess oil and transfer it 
  into a dish. Shankarpali is ready.
• You can store them in an air tight container when they cool down completely. They have shelf life 
  of about 1 month.

 Malini finds out that Aradhana is her first daughter, and she gets shocked after knowing the truth. She hugs her and promises to give her all the love and affection that she deserves. A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. snippet.description:

Tapu Sena plans to play night cricket. Bapuji has told Tapu not to trouble anyone. Tapu is angry at Goli's brother. Goli's brother has come to play cricket with them.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 0175
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3922: Jetha Ka Zabardast Surprise
--------------------------------------------------------
Bagha and Nattu Kakka persuade Jetha that he should have a small get-together as he is going to announce a big surprise for Babita. Jethalal invites everyone to the clubhouse in the evening and tells Babita he has a huge surprise in store for her. He also keeps pizza and ice cream in the clubhouse for the society members. When everyone learns of Jethalal's surprise, how will they all respond? Watch the episode to find out what happens 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3922, 7 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 381
snippet.description:
സ്വന്തമായി വീട് ഇല്ലാത്തതിനെ കുറിച്ചുള്ള ചർച്ചയിലാണ് ലച്ചുവും, കേശുവും, ശിവാനിയും, പാറുവും. പത്താം ക്ലാസ്സിൽ മുഴുവൻ മാർക്കും വാങ്ങി സ്വന്തം വീട്ടിൽ കയറണം എന്നതാണ് ശിവാനിയുടെ ആഗ്രഹം. മക്കളുടെ ചോദ്യങ്ങൾക്കു മുൻപിൽ നിസ്സഹായരായി ബാലുവും നീലുവും!

Lachu, Keshu, Shivani and Paru are having a discussion on not having a house of their own. Shivani's biggest dream is to step into her own house after scoring flashy marks in tenth grade. Balu and Neelu seem to be helpless when confronted by their children!

snippet.title: 12th Fail - New Trailer | A Tale Of Triumph | Vidhu Vinod Chopra | Vikrant Massey | In Cinemas Only
snippet.description:
12th Fail is an incredible, inspiring real life story of a boy from Chambal who aims to achieve an impossible dream of passing the world’s toughest civil services entrance exam, that of the Union Public Service Commission.

Watch #12thFail in cinemas now - inspired by a million true stories.

Vinod Chopra Films
in association with
Zee Studios
presents

Baylagaam Episode 31 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 8th November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

The story centers around Ramsha, a young girl and the only child of her loving parents, Sajid and Mehnaz. Raised with affection and no restrictions, Ramsha enjoys unlimited internet access, which leads to her spending an excessive time on social media, quickly becoming her hobby.
As her fascination with social media intensifies, Ramsha's hobby evolves into an all-consuming passion for fame, prompting her to take extreme measures. During her relentless pursuit of stardom, she crosses paths with Afnan, the son of the influential businessman Qasim Ali. While Afnan, who holds affection for his paternal cousin Aleezay, views Ramsha as a source of amusement, she misinterprets their friendship as love.
Disheartened by her failed search for love, Ramsha turns towards fame. Ramsha's unwavering quest for popularity propels her onto a challenging path, causing turmoil within her family. As her popularity soars, she becomes increasingly distant from her loved ones, leading her life down a tumultuous road, where she discovers the other side of fame many people are unaware of. Along this journey, she encounters Afnan once more, but circumstances have taken a different turn.
Will Ramsha achieve the fame she so desperately desires? Will her pursuit bring dire consequences? Can she find contentment in fame instead of love? And will Ramsha's parents have to bear the consequences of her passion?

The story centers around Ramsha, a young girl and the only child of her loving parents, Sajid and Mehnaz. Raised with affection and no restrictions, Ramsha enjoys unlimited internet access, which leads to her spending an excessive time on social media, quickly becoming her hobby.
As her fascination with social media intensifies, Ramsha's hobby evolves into an all-consuming passion for fame, prompting her to take extreme measures. During her relentless pursuit of stardom, she crosses paths with Afnan, the son of the influential businessman Qasim Ali. While Afnan, who holds affection for his paternal cousin Aleezay, views Ramsha as a source of amusement, she misinterprets their friendship as love.
Disheartened by her failed search for love, Ramsha turns towards fame. Ramsha's unwavering quest for popularity propels her onto a challenging path, causing turmoil within her family. As her popularity soars, she becomes increasingly distant from her loved ones, leading her life down a tumultuous road, where she discovers the other side of fame many people are unaware of. Along this journey, she encounters Afnan once more, but circumstances have taken a different turn.
Will Ramsha achieve the fame she so desperately desires? Will her pursuit bring dire consequences? Can she find contentment in fame instead of love? And will Ramsha's parents have to bear the consequences of her passion?

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Mannat Murad Episode 12 - [Eng Sub] - Iqra Aziz - Talha Chahour - Digitally Presented by PEL - 6th November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Mannat Murad Digitally Presented by PEL

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

On the other hand, Murad belongs to a conservative family where his mother, the matriarch, wields significant influence over his life choices. As the only son, Murad is burdened with the responsibility of fulfilling his family's expectations. Soft-spoken and romantic by nature, Murad finds himself unable to defy his mother's authority, especially after the passing of his father.

Despite their starkly contrasting backgrounds, Mannat and Murad's hearts find solace in each other's presence, and they fall deeply in love. However, their families' interference creates misunderstandings between Mannat and Murad, testing the strength of their bond.

Will their families agree to their union? Will Mannat's family, with their open-mindedness, find common ground with Murad's conservative household? Can Mannat and Murad's love for each other withstand the motives of their families, who seek to create further misunderstandings between them?

Maa Nahi Saas Hoon Main Episode 06 - [Eng Sub] - Hammad Shoaib - Sumbul Iqbal - Farhan Ally Agha - 8th November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

This story revolves around Mehreen and her daughter Areej, who was born after years of prayers. Prior to her birth, Mehreen and her husband had been caring for Salman, Areej's cousin. However, a tragedy struck, separating Areej from her family. Afterwards, Mehreen decided to raise Salman as her own son.
Years later, Salman crosses paths with Urooj, a beautiful and fearless girl, the daughter of school teacher Shoaib and his wife Naseem. Initially resistant to Salman's advances, Urooj eventually falls in love with him. Unbeknownst to Salman and his family, Urooj is none other than Areej, Mehreen's long-lost daughter.
Will Urooj discover the truth about her identity? How will the family come to know that Urooj is Mehreen’s long-lost daughter, Areej? How will Urooj react when she gets to know that Mehreen is her real mother? What impact will Urooj’s identity have on Salman? Will Mehreen accept Urooj as her daughter? Maa Nahi Saas Hoon Main Episode 06 - [Eng Sub] - Hammad Shoaib - Sumbul Iqbal - Farhan Ally Agha - 8th November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

This story revolves around Mehreen and her daughter Areej, who was born after years of prayers. Prior to her birth, Mehreen and her husband had been caring for Salman, Areej's cousin. However, a tragedy struck, separating Areej from her family. Afterwards, Mehreen decided to raise Salman as her own son.
Years later, Salman crosses paths with Urooj, a beautiful and fearless girl, the daughter of school teacher Shoaib and his wife Naseem. Initially resistant to Salman's advances, Urooj eventually falls in love with him. Unbeknownst to Salman and his family, Urooj is none other than Areej, Mehreen's long-lost daughter.
Will Urooj discover the truth about her identity? How will the family come to know that Urooj is Mehreen’s long-lost daughter, Areej? How will Urooj react when she gets to know that Mehreen is her real mother? What impact will Urooj’s identity have on Salman? Will Mehreen accept Urooj as her daughter? Will Urooj’s true identity pose a threat to her relationship with Salman?

snippet.title: Jethalal ने की एक Pani Puri वाले से कैसी Deal? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chasmah | Pani Puri
snippet.description:
Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Bagha and Nattu Kaka try to convince Jethalal to follow their tips to grow the sales of Gada Electronics. Jethalal visits a Pani Puri Shop, recommended by Nattu Kaka. Jetha likes the Pani Puri a lot and wants to do a deal with him. Watch the full episode. 

Show Name : Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast: Kush Shah, Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode No: 2571
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#comedy2023 #comedy #jethalal #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch the specially curated series of Pani Puri:
https://studio.youtube.com/playlist/PLSXTaG1fT0cQEuCKKlujcVJPbbmUKJMKD/edit
